c: 16
v: 112
t: "Ndipo Mulungu wapereka chitsanzo cha Mzinda umene udali wabata ndi wamtendere, chakudya chake chidali chambiri chimene chimachokera kumbali zosiyanasiyana koma anthu ake adakana zokoma za Mulungu. Kotero Mulungu adaulawitsa Mzindawo vuto la njala ndi mantha chifukwa cha zimene iwo amachita"